h6. Feature Request Description
It will be great to have a feature that can automatically send notification emails to some groups/users (such as managers) when logged work exceeds original estimate in one issue, and at the same time generate a private comment to the Assignee in that ticket to remind him about the over work log.

h6. Workaround
However, for send out the notification emails to some groups/users (such as managers) when logged work exceeds original estimate in one issue. Here is a current workaround:
# Type the following query by using Advanced Search in Issue Navigator:
{noformat}
workratio >= 100
{noformat}
This is for all projects, if you only willing to search for certain projects, you can specify the project in the advanced search.
For example:
{noformat}
project = testing AND workratio >= 100
{noformat}
